{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"fccaed3e05","title":"在听取钱信忠、张凯汇报卫生工作时的谈话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"9b0768d9c6","index":0,"year":1965,"month":8,"day":2,"articleId":"fccaed3e05","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"对话","id":"314ad57c4d","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"医药卫生","id":"b55010d172","type":"主题"},{"name":"关键人物文稿","id":"c20d333791","type":"文稿大类"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"e2305b9e63","type":"主题"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"ee69e1def3","type":"title","text":"在听取钱信忠、张凯汇报卫生工作时的谈话","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fccaed3e05","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7c0c22752f","type":"paragraph","text":"在听取钱信忠、张凯汇报卫生工作时的谈话","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fccaed3e05","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d0fe148e2c","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fccaed3e05","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"28aa87b6bd","type":"paragraph","text":"1965.08.02","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fccaed3e05","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e3527953dc","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：我要讲的都讲了。你们打算怎么办？","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fccaed3e05","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d45cd4c213","type":"paragraph","text":"答：（略。汇报到打算为农村生产队培训不脱产卫生员）","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fccaed3e05","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"cb6093de11","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：训练多长时间？","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fccaed3e05","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d9da447e6e","type":"paragraph","text":"答：半个月左右。","index":7,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fccaed3e05","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2dc643045a","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：半个月太短了吧！","index":8,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fccaed3e05","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"436885d300","type":"paragraph","text":"答：他们主要学会些针灸，常见病的治疗和一些预防工作，训练后还要带他们做。","index":9,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fccaed3e05","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"be3ef53dca","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：带很重要，带多长时间？","index":10,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fccaed3e05","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ebd0ab4b6b","type":"paragraph","text":"答：城市医疗队下去可一直带，共带三、四个月。","index":11,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fccaed3e05","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ddee236806","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：这还可以，带三、四个月，学会治十几种病。","index":12,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fccaed3e05","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"06bd17a770","type":"paragraph","text":"（当汇报到搞了一些半农半读训练班时。）","index":13,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fccaed3e05","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"267f301261","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：半农半读怎么搞法？","index":14,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fccaed3e05","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"02955eaee3","type":"paragraph","text":"答：采取农忙不学，农闲多学的方式。","index":15,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fccaed3e05","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"13f5b28373","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：多长时间？","index":16,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fccaed3e05","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"03cd9e84a8","type":"paragraph","text":"答：两年，三年。","index":17,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fccaed3e05","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c1f6f9c14b","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：两年就是读一年书，三年就是读一年半书，这个办法好。","index":18,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fccaed3e05","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"96c0046dc3","type":"paragraph","text":"（当汇报到根据毛的指示卫生部作了检查时。）","index":19,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fccaed3e05","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"fd66eb9660","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：现在有多少卫生技术人员？","index":20,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fccaed3e05","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d7c01eb8e1","type":"paragraph","text":"答：（略）","index":21,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fccaed3e05","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"053c472266","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：这个队伍不小！","index":22,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fccaed3e05","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4cd6e8e44b","type":"paragraph","text":"汇报：主席批评我们只为城市人口服务，很对。现在高级医务人员百分之八十在城市，其中百分之七十在大城市，百分之二十在县城，只有百分之十在农村。经费，包括县在内，农村占百分之二十五，百分之七十五用在城市。","index":23,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fccaed3e05","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"fb52957b43","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：你们用了这么多人力、这么多钱，为那么少的人服务。","index":24,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fccaed3e05","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"14843c5b69","type":"paragraph","text":"答：主席指示后，才清醒了。","index":25,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fccaed3e05","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ace839e80b","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：你们研究过神医没有？","index":26,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fccaed3e05","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a59f94514c","type":"paragraph","text":"答：我们没有研究过。","index":27,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fccaed3e05","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"881b445088","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：神医有个好处：神药它保险，不会害人，没有毒；第二个好处是省钱，几个铜板就可以了；第三是给病人精神安慰，病也就好了。","index":28,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fccaed3e05","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a001a3a4dc","type":"paragraph","text":"答：许多病不治也可以好。","index":29,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fccaed3e05","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c6b44e3efd","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：比骗人的医生要好。","index":30,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fccaed3e05","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"90335291d6","type":"paragraph","text":"汇报：通过四清和医疗队下乡，了解到农村卫生队伍很复杂。","index":31,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fccaed3e05","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"56d48d3995","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：怎么复杂？","index":32,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fccaed3e05","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1967a4eb45","type":"paragraph","text":"答：有许多人过去不是医生，看些医书就加入到医务人员队伍里来了。","index":33,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fccaed3e05","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"06bbc62bba","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：看些什么书？","index":34,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fccaed3e05","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7d86a6928c","type":"paragraph","text":"答：看些中医书，看些药方。农村医务队伍中，政治情况复杂，技术水平低的占百分之四十左右。","index":35,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fccaed3e05","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1086abefe1","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：坏人不多吧？","index":36,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fccaed3e05","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f668062791","type":"paragraph","text":"答：真正坏人占百分之五左右，但政治技术水平低的较多，占百分之四十左右，这个队伍如果没有新生力量，取消他们还不容易。","index":37,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fccaed3e05","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4e69cb6a11","type":"paragraph","text":"汇报：现在正在召开医学教育会议，讨论主席、总理指示，要办三年制卫生学校，为农村培养医生。","index":38,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fccaed3e05","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"181a24e639","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：高等教育要五年，读那么长时间书，值得研究。","index":39,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fccaed3e05","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"64d8057eff","type":"paragraph","text":"汇报：现在想两条腿走路，办三年制，多在农村办，在农村招生。","index":40,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fccaed3e05","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"084488ed83","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：招什么生？","index":41,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fccaed3e05","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e7b2c4273f","type":"paragraph","text":"答：大部分招高中生。","index":42,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fccaed3e05","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2b310f8cd3","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：初中生还不行吗？","index":43,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fccaed3e05","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4e9841637d","type":"paragraph","text":"答：目前农村高中生还不少。","index":44,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fccaed3e05","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0da550b85c","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：招中学生还不行吗？你们不在城市招了吗？","index":45,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fccaed3e05","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"81c88095ac","type":"paragraph","text":"答：城市也招一些，主要在农村招。","index":46,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fccaed3e05","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"cb26cc3ed0","type":"paragraph","text":"（当谈到医生政治思想最重要，只有技术没有政治不行时）","index":47,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fccaed3e05","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c4d3d36428","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：这一点很重要。医生一定要政治好，招些政治好的中学生就可以了。","index":48,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fccaed3e05","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5fd6988df7","type":"paragraph","text":"汇报到城市问题时。","index":49,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fccaed3e05","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b5abcdf6f5","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：你们对城市是不是服务得好？","index":50,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fccaed3e05","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ffbfa2a80d","type":"paragraph","text":"答：也没有服务好，要求愈来愈高。","index":51,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fccaed3e05","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c2dab209c9","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：怎么愈来愈高？","index":52,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fccaed3e05","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f801170f0a","type":"paragraph","text":"答：以北京来讲，××多万干部公费医疗，××多万工人劳保，还有家属。","index":53,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fccaed3e05","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7a7236d709","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：工人不是“老爷”，工人还是要为他们服务的。","index":54,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fccaed3e05","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f31eea1dfd","type":"paragraph","text":"汇报：工厂医务工作没有搞好，工人也都到医院去看病。","index":55,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fccaed3e05","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5770f9904c","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：你们为什么不在工厂设不脱产卫生员呢？小厂可以设卫生员，大厂设医务所。","index":56,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fccaed3e05","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f0a2384861","type":"paragraph","text":"答：非正式医生开不了假条，要请假还要到医院去，经医生开证明才行。","index":57,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fccaed3e05","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7df906ddf3","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：这涉及到劳保问题，要好好考虑。","index":58,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fccaed3e05","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"93a5054142","type":"paragraph","text":"答：城市医院压力很大，公费医疗包下来，一个钱不出，到处看病。","index":59,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fccaed3e05","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"cbe3860495","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：看了病，拿了药还不吃。","index":60,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fccaed3e05","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e50009a3fb","type":"paragraph","text":"汇报：总理指示城市要组织医务人员下农村，每年去三分之一。","index":61,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fccaed3e05","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"eba4acc960","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：怎么下去，多久？","index":62,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fccaed3e05","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3e9b26fabc","type":"paragraph","text":"答：轮流下去。下去后城市医疗卫生工作仍比较重。我们打算高等医学院校学生三年就一边工作一边上课。护士也一面工作一面学习。","index":63,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fccaed3e05","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e2c38ef4b8","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：光念念书是不行的。你们对打仗考虑了没有？","index":64,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fccaed3e05","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1de81ce4a6","type":"paragraph","text":"答：中央指示后考虑的。","index":65,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fccaed3e05","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e4fdaf8b26","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：怎么考虑的。","index":66,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fccaed3e05","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"96fd8766d0","type":"paragraph","text":"答：组织了××个医疗队，随时准备赴前线服务。现在的医院对战争没有训练。组织医疗队训练，有的地方已开始了。","index":67,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fccaed3e05","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"064dd111e5","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：打仗了还能都到北京医院看病？要考虑到打仗。你们分科那么细，打起仗来怎么办？打起仗来还不是什么都要看，只会内科不会外科怎么行？","index":68,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fccaed3e05","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d79d68edc6","type":"paragraph","text":"答：过去部队年轻人多，疑难病可能不多，有的也许不认识。但是医学科学是发展的，要有一小部分力量搞尖端。","index":69,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fccaed3e05","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9c03c63568","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：搞科研的人看不看病？","index":70,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fccaed3e05","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"751bbb752c","type":"paragraph","text":"答：一部分人看病，一部分人不看病。","index":71,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fccaed3e05","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7edaeee01f","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：什么人不看病。","index":72,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fccaed3e05","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7a857f6c5d","type":"paragraph","text":"答：搞基础科学的，如搞生理、药理、生化的，研究理论不看病。","index":73,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fccaed3e05","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3b0e4497fe","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：理论还是要结合实际啊！","index":74,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fccaed3e05","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a33612f2ba","type":"paragraph","text":"答：×××同志说百分之五搞尖端就可以了，现在共有科研队伍××人，其中技术队伍××人。","index":75,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fccaed3e05","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c39bf21d4f","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：科学尖端还是要搞的。","index":76,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fccaed3e05","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e12c6c438a","type":"paragraph","text":"请示：第一，卫生员的工分问题。人民公社六十条规定，补贴工分不超过百分之二，卫生员的补贴工分社员同意给，但六十条没有规定。","index":77,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fccaed3e05","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a0f58e1123","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：给群众办好事没问题，农民会同意的。现在干部参加了劳动，百分之二也用不了，有的地方只用百分之一。工分不成问题，农民会同意的。","index":78,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fccaed3e05","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3b67c04802","type":"paragraph","text":"请示：第二个问题，希望党委多领导、批评我们，多抓卫生工作。我们认识到党委多抓、多领导、批评，工作才有劲。","index":79,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fccaed3e05","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"90491c5819","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：这话很对。党委是集体领导，什么都要管。卫生部门是为人民服务的，当然要抓，党委也要研究卫生工作。","index":80,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fccaed3e05","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"33b3fa097e","type":"paragraph","text":"最近政治局不是要讨论卫生工作吗？你们的报告写得怎么样了？写好，送政治局。","index":81,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fccaed3e05","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0fac54551d","type":"paragraph","text":"请示：农村卫生工作是个很重要的问题，建议中央今年召开一个农村卫生工作会议，中央召开可以找省市领导同志参加。","index":82,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fccaed3e05","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3c63468d45","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：可以。","index":83,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fccaed3e05","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7d49f5c927","type":"paragraph","text":"请示：还有有关药的问题。","index":84,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fccaed3e05","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f362dc6605","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：药的问题怎么样？","index":85,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fccaed3e05","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b16eea7482","type":"paragraph","text":"答：药不归卫生部门管，问题不少，现在正在研究解决。","index":86,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fccaed3e05","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9c9ba8d3eb","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：药品应当降价。","index":87,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fccaed3e05","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"71ab10de25","type":"paragraph","text":"汇报：药品降价对农民有一定的好处。但药主要用在城市，药降价，农民还是看不起病。","index":88,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fccaed3e05","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5068654569","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：天津计划生育不要钱。看来国家出了钱，实际是划得来的。国家出点钱保护生产力是合算的，药钱拿不起也可以不拿。你们开展农村卫生工作后，要搞节制生育。","index":89,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fccaed3e05","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"fdb4ebf81a","type":"paragraph","text":"答：我们医疗队下去也搞计划生育。","index":90,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fccaed3e05","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1b835a0390","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：农民接受得如何？","index":91,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fccaed3e05","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3efc4b844b","type":"paragraph","text":"答：宣传后可以接受。","index":92,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fccaed3e05","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"cec4577e17","type":"paragraph","text":"最后，请示主席还有什么指示。","index":93,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fccaed3e05","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"17cf6659d0","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：没有什么了，就按你们讲的办吧！","index":94,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fccaed3e05","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}